<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:0.00px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">---</span><span class="cls_009">以下單字請自行練習發音</span><span class="cls_008">---</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:19.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">ビートルズ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:368.40px;top:19.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">披頭四</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_009">英國著名的樂團</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:27.60px;top:56.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">ぶん けい</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:60.60px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">文型</span></div>
