<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:101.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">わたしの  趣味は  映画を  見る  ことです。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:69.60px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">ね</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:159.60px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">にっ  き</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:214.80px;top:118.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">か</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:38.40px;top:121.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">3.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:121.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">寝る  まえに、日記を  書きます。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:27.60px;top:158.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">れい ぶん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:162.60px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">例文</span></div>
