<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:473.34px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">コピーが</span><span class="cls_008">  </span><span class="cls_009">できます</span><span class="cls_008">  （ 1</span><span class="cls_009">枚</span><span class="cls_008">  10</span><span class="cls_009">円</span><span class="cls_008"> ）</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:122.40px;top:490.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">と  しょ  かん</span></div>
